企业。”<br />3.“紧跟党中央，为党和人民的事业努力奋斗” 是海航的”行动指南“。 <a href=\"https://t.co/7PvpMDuZDV\">https://t.co/7PvpMDuZDV</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; KurikoC (@kuriko_c) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/kuriko_c/status/961575108455424000?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 8, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p> <script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script> </p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-lang=\"en\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">2月7日海航全体党员大会，董事局长陈峰讲话称海航的事业”是党的事业、人民的事业、全人类的事业“，海航“始终把自己当做一滴水，融入民族社会和国家的海洋里”。海航旗下各企业党委书记会上分别表态：坚定不移跟党走，维护党和国家发展成果。大会在《国际歌》中胜利闭幕。详见：<a href=\"https://t.co/txxNqlxYu6\">https://t.co/txxNqlxYu6</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/3UIER3jg4y\">pic.twitter.com/3UIER3jg4y</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; KurikoC (@kuriko_c) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/kuriko_c/status/961561248398741504?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 8, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p> <script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script> </p>\n<p><strong><em>敬请点击<a href=\"https://github.com/yinghuocho/firefly-proxy\">这里</a>下载翻墙利器萤火虫代理，<a href=\"https://github.com/yinghuocho/download/blob/master/firefly_windows_386_install.exe?raw=true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Windows版</a>，<a href=\"https://github.com/yinghuocho/download/blob/master/firefly_darwin_amd64_install.dmg?raw=true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mac版</a>，<a href=\"https://github.com/yinghuocho/download/blob/master/firefly.apk?raw=true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">安卓手机版</a>和<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/cn/app/%E5%B0%BC%E9%A9%AC%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86/id1260125306?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">iPhone/iPad版</a>。</em></strong></p>\n","author":972,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,28589,27949],"tags":[33106,33930]}